flow.descriptionCdata:
be63d032-30de-459b-830f-f8cb09e03aa2.description=
This workflow deploys the DMA workflow on the target server

Inputs\:

coreHost		- The DNS name or IP address of the the SA host
corePort		- The port to connect to SA core
coreUsername	- The username for the  HP SA host
corePassword	- The password for the  HP SA host
organizationName	- Name of the CSA organization associated with the service request
targetHostname	- DNS name of the target server to be added to the DMA organization
dmaWorkflowName	- Name of the DMA workflow to be deployed on the target server
resOffrProps		- List of property Names and values on the resource offering
		  E.g. property 1;value1,value2|property 2;value3|property 3;value3,value4|........

Responses\:
success - Workflow completed successfully.
failure - Something went wrong.
flow.name: DMA Application Deployment
